Comment: 0,0:01:42.07,0:01:45.56,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Oops! I killed another morning
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.56,0:01:50.01,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}一個人天花板 盯著的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:54.22,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}包羅萬象什麼的 無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:56.39,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}腦袋裡面載入
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:01:58.52,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}是不是不可能的嘛
Comment: 0,0:01:58.52,0:02:00.36,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Go ask my instincts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.70,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}一直響著的沉默的警鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.92,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}那又是誰的規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.92,0:02:26.52,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}不要迷茫跳進去跳進去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.52,0:02:28.88,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}站起來 破壞掉這無理的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:30.47,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}如果解不開這沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.47,0:02:32.89,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}就大喊露鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:35.22,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}直到終幕我都要說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:38.09,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Gear up! 這不是玩笑
Comment: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:40.95,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Nighty night
Comment: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:41.63,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Oh baby
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.63,0:02:44.15,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}去捨棄掉吧 rulers
Comment: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:45.98,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}I’m my only ruler
Comment: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:47.07,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}One day…
Comment: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:54.92,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}I’m my only ruler
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:31.60,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,波打つざわめき
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:35.12,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,彩度を失う記憶に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:39.71,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,願いは幾度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:42.47,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,数えてみたって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:44.16,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,震えている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:47.94,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,晦冥を揺らしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:51.18,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,希望に似てた歌を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:54.80,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,祈れば砂のように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:58.33,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,零れ落ちる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:02.00,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,ずっと知っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:05.39,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,密かに息吹く想い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:09.18,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,錆びついた鋼に触れて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:13.41,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,意味もなく　際限なく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:15.32,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,廻るの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:20.10,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,世界が引き裂かれても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.10,0:22:23.83,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,結んだ手離さずいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.16,0:22:28.26,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,歪んだ支配が朽ちても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.26,0:22:29.94,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,その名を呼ぶの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.94,0:22:33.97,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,綺麗なアイじゃなくっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:37.92,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,息をするたびに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:41.98,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,あなた求めてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:46.21,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,どこへはぐれてしまっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:48.45,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:31.60,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,起起落落的雜音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:35.12,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,在失去色彩的記憶中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:39.71,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,祈求了多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:42.47,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,只是數一數
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:44.16,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,也混身震顫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:47.94,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,像是那波動黑暗的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:51.18,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,希望似的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.51,0:21:54.80,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,祈禱的話就會像沙礫一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:58.33,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,凋零飄落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:02.00,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,我一直都知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:05.39,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,那呼吸中不為人知的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:09.18,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,接觸到了生鏽的鋼鐵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.18,0:22:13.41,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,沒有意義 沒有終點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.41,0:22:15.32,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,循環
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:20.10,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,就算世界崩裂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.10,0:22:23.83,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,我們握緊的手也不會分開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.16,0:22:28.26,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,就算扭曲的統治腐朽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.26,0:22:29.94,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,我也會呼喚那個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.94,0:22:33.97,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,就算不是美麗的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:37.92,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,我只要一息尚存
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:41.98,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,便在尋求著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:46.21,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,無論迷失在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:48.45,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,再一次
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
